data.description: Beautiful seasonal lakeview Eden Isle home located on the prestigious Red Apple Golf Course.  This home features 5 large bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, a private office, theater room and large storage room.  Three of the bedrooms have private bathrooms attached.  The remaining two bedrooms are connected via a Jack and Jill Bathroom.  All of the bedrooms currently have King sized beds.  The downstairs features a large kitchen and family room overlooking the golf course, separate formal dining and wet bar.  The Master bathroom was recently renovated with new cabinets with granite counter tops, two sinks, two smart mirrors, large walking-in custom shower with electronic water controls.  The home features 2 large front porches, new landscaping with sprinkler system, two car garage and covered porch overlooking the golf course.  This property is agent owned.
